#

Chocolate Milkshake

5 min
$3.5
500 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Dessert

Tags:

DessertBeverageSweet

Description

A rich and creamy chocolate milkshake that’s perfect for satisfying your sweet tooth in minutes!

Ingredients

  • chocolate ice cream: 2 cups
  • milk: 1 cup
  • chocolate syrup: 3 tablespoons
  • whipped cream: optional, for topping
  • chocolate shavings or sprinkles: optional, for garnish
